...focused on selling
their products

00:22:00.385 --> 00:22:02.554
in the growing Chinese market.

00:22:02.620 --> 00:22:05.523
&gt;&gt; We have actually a, a very
special Italian wine.

00:22:05.590 --> 00:22:08.292
The cream of the top
of the Italian wines.

00:22:08.359 --> 00:22:10.395 line:0%
&gt;&gt; SULLIVAN: U.S. companies have
