00:22:14.232 --> 00:22:17.234 line:0%
&gt;&gt; China is going to be
number-one market

00:22:17.301 --> 00:22:20.138 line:0%
from any perspective, and...

00:22:20.205 --> 00:22:21.672 line:0%
&gt;&gt; SULLIVAN: For G.E.
or for everybody?

00:22:21.739 --> 00:22:22.941 line:0%
&gt;&gt; For, for everybody.

00:22:23.008 --> 00:22:25.643 line:0%
&gt;&gt; SULLIVAN: With 1.4 billion
customers,

00:22:25.710 --> 00:22:30.582 line:0%
China's a market U.S. companies
