00:22:30.649 --> 00:22:32.817 line:0%
&gt;&gt; We've been in the China
market for 34 years.

00:22:32.884 --> 00:22:36.487 line:0%
We have over 40 wholly owned
or joint-venture subsidiaries

00:22:36.554 --> 00:22:38.323
in the market.

00:22:38.390 --> 00:22:41.359 line:0%
So very, very important to
DuPont.

00:22:41.426 --> 00:22:43.561 line:0%
&gt;&gt; SULLIVAN: It seemed like
business as usual.

00:22:43.628 --> 00:22:46.131 line:0%
So what do you think
