00:22:48.500 --> 00:22:51.335 line:0%
to not worry about, because
today I met myriads

00:22:51.402 --> 00:22:53.604 line:0%
of Chinese businesspeople...

00:22:53.671 --> 00:22:55.773
&gt;&gt; SULLIVAN: Okay.
&gt;&gt; ...men and women,

00:22:55.840 --> 00:22:57.175
that look you in the eye,

00:22:57.242 --> 00:22:58.709
and they want to do business
with you.

00:22:58.776 --> 00:23:00.945
&gt;&gt; SULLIVAN: They do. &gt;&gt; And
you're going to find a way.

00:23:01.012 --> 00:23:02.247
&gt;&gt; SULLIVAN: It was hard to
gauge if Trump's tariffs

00:23:02.314 --> 00:23:03.948
